<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5027872>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. External morphology of Anthopleura mariscali, new species. Scale bar = 0.5 mm. A. Partially contracted live specimen. Note striped appearance of distal column and well­expanded marginal projections with verrucae. Photograph by C. P. Hickman, Jr. B. Holotype. Note spots of dark pigment on tips of some tentacles and marginal projections." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5027872/files/figure.png" .

